                    "reviewer_name": "Dan",
                    "comments": "Trisha was very proactive with communication, coordinating the meeting for our arrival and departure. She provided us with many tips for places to dine and shop around Coyoac\u00e1n, and we enjoyed all of the ones we tried (which was most of them). She's also simply a very cool and caring person, and I wish we would have spent more time talking.\n\nThe home is beautiful and feels very secure. It's right around the corner from Museo Frida Kahlo and just a few minutes walk to many other things. Getting an Uber is super quick and inexpensive if you need to visit other neighborhoods, which we did daily. \n\nWe would stay here again in a heartbeat and thoroughly recommend booking with Trisha if you're looking to stay in Coyoac\u00e1n."
