                    "reviewerid": "797194",
                    "reviewer_name": "Cristina",
                    "comments": "If you are heading to Coyoacan for a few days  to explore Frida\u2019s Blue House, Trotsky Museum and various other museums, cultural centers, and an amazing theater complex, then do stay at Trisha\u2019s studio  - a comfortable, bright and fully-equipped apt in a great location.   In addition, Trisha is a wonderful hostess who will go out of her way to make your stay just perfect!"
