               "host_about": "If you're anything like us, then you most likely love to travel around the world, savoring the most extraordinary foods and wines and encountering all the amazing spots a new place has to offer out-of-towners.\r\n\r\nWithout a doubt, you also enjoy getting to feel the essence of a vernacular culture while staying at high-end, luxurious, centrally located, comfortable retreats. But most importantly, I bet you really prefer doing so without having to pay the price tag for all you are receiving and that's what we call being a \"Smart Travel Decision Maker\".\r\n\r\nWell, we have some very good news for you today, since our splendid \"Non-Smoking Residencies and Studios\" located at the heart of Mexico\u00b4s capital, are all about that and had been recently made accessible to savvy travelers like you. \r\n\r\nHi there! We are Jorge & Monnah and we really like to make new friends, especially people from outside Mexico.  We've been traveling around the world for quite some time now. We are a family of 4 currently living in breath-taking Canc\u00fan, MEXICO. We have this marvelous properties in Mexico City that we really love for its history in our family and every time we go to our Big City, we enjoy enormously staying at any of them. We love and enjoy M\u00e9xico City like few other places in the whole world. These unique accommodations are available now with all sort of amenities and services to assure a comfortable stay to our important guests. We are very accommodating hosts so if any of our guests needs anything, we are always willing to help; so please don't hesitate to ask...\r\n\r\nWe're sure that you and your travel companions will also enjoy your next trip to Mexico the way you never anticipated, should you resolve to come over and stay at any of our gorgeous properties. So we encourage you to make yourself your own \"Smart Travel Decision\" and enjoy your upcoming adventure in wonderful M\u00e9xico City like you never thought possible by making our home your home. \r\n\r\nMi casa es su casa!\r\n\r\nSincerely, \r\n\r\nJorge & Monnah",
