                    "date": "2015-11-02",
                    "reviewerid": "565835",
                    "reviewer_name": "Richard",
                    "comments": "Our stay at Paco and Maria's house was absolutely perfect.  The house is large and very comfortable.  The house was very secure, neat, and clean.  The area is safe and convenient.  If I return to Mexico City I would definitely stay here again.  They get 5 stars from me.    They even provided a cell phone for us to use while in the city.  Very handy to have a phone as we needed to call our driver to pick us up during our tours of the city.  Don't hesitate to stay here, you won't be disappointed.  If you do stay here and you don't feel like heading out too far for dinner you should try La Poblanita de Tacobaya.  Take a left as you exit the house then take your 1st left at the corner and head down 2 blocks.  Restaurant is on your left.  Very good food.  Also, there's a very good burger place directly across from La Poblanita.  The Bayou.  Kind of a hipster small burger joint.  Let me tell you, I think I had one of the best burgers I ever had there.  We ate there one night as La Poblanita closed at 7pm.  Thank you Paco and Maria for providing an awesome place to stay.  I hope to see you guys again.\r\n\r\nRich"
