                    "comments": "Roberto's place is absolutely stunning -- even better than I expected. It truly is like stepping into a timewarp. The built in cabinets, the tulip table, the Bertoia chairs -- all of this stuff is original and really, really beautiful. I was here for 2 weeks, and the place began to feel like home. It's a huge space, and definitely one of the most unique airbnb's I've ever been in. Roberto was as helpful as he could possibly be. When the internet wasn't quite as fast as I needed it to be (I work in software development), he immediately called to have the bandwidth increased. When I locked myself out of the apartment, he was there in 10 minutes with the keys. This airbnb is exactly what I'm looking for when I go to DF.  I'll certainly be coming back here to stay."
