                    "comments": "This place is in a seriously awesome location. (Coffee shop downstairs, park up the road, supermarket across the road, everything within 2-5 minutes of walking). We never actually met Morgana, but the entire stay was stress-free and easy. The apartment is well-sized, clean and not too noisy. (We were staying with an 11 month old!) Really easy stay, would absolutely recommend it and would love to stay here again."
