                    "reviewer_name": "Kyle",
                    "comments": "Just like a suite at the W Hotel, except better amenities and WAAY less expensive!\r\n\r\n\r\nTHE APARTMENT //\r\n\r\nMay not look to impressive from the outside, but lives up to the billing once you get in...\r\n\r\nCLEAN :: a new bar of soap in the bathroom and great towels.\r\nWELL APPOINTED :: modern / minimalist design, great kitchen\r\nSAFE :: the outer lock is like something from a sci-fi movie\r\n\r\n\r\nTHE LOCATION //\r\n\r\nI'm an early 30s young professional looking to hang out in the hipper neighborhoods in town, see art / architecture and hang out at the cooler bars. The neighborhood is fine, not really where I wanted to spend my time, but I felt completely safe (even stumbling home at 3:00 AM)... But the beauty of the location is that it's (Phone number hidden by Airbnb) minute walk to the best neighborhoods in the city Roma & Condesa.\r\n\r\n\r\nTHE HOST //\r\n\r\nFrancisco was amazing! He let me in early to drop my luggage. Waited for me when I got lost (btw... Don't trust (Hidden by Airbnb) maps to show you this address it's two blocks off) and recommended hip/fun bars to check out."
