                    "comments": "I with my wife and 2 years old daughter stayed at  Francisco & Rodolfo's apartment in June 2018. The check-in was great,  Francisco was already waiting us in the apartment. We took Uber from the airport, no issues. The apartment was exactly as described. Wifi signal was strong and I was able to watch Mundial games without lugging. We loved the location, very close to downtown and the biggest park in the city where we loved to spend our time (we spend entire three days to cover the area). There are great food places around (El Califa, where you can find great tacos and Yug , if you like vegetarian).  Exchange just 2 min away with great rates 19-20,  don't change in the airport at 16-17. My daughter got a fewer during the stay and  Francisco & Rodolfo allowed us to extend our check out understanding the case. They are a great hosts and I will highly recommend the place for couple (+ baby).  Thanks for your hospitality and doing it.  All the best!"
