                    "reviewerid": "1473875",
                    "reviewer_name": "Jay",
                    "comments": "It's a great deal in a very real neighborhood, close to both the city bus lines and the Hospital General green line metro. There are plenty of little shops, the taqueria on the corner is excellent, and there is even night life nearby. Accommodations are spartan but clean, with a refrigerator, microwave and wireless internet right in the room, which is a self-contained little world up top of the building. Jackie and family are friendly and attentive, but it's possible to go days as I did without having to check in for anything. Recommended! Jay Dunn"
