                    "comments": "We had a truly wonderful time staying with Paco, his wife, and his two adorable dogs. As promised, Paco was there when we arrived, and gave us a very comprehensive \"orientation\" to the city. His apartment is gorgeous and located in a neighborhood that always felt safe and is conveniently located close to both Condesa and La Roma--our two favorite areas. It's also located close to a few different subway lines, which we used several times during our stay. It's also located near a \"formal\" taxi stand, which was very convenient. Paco provided a great breakfast every morning--coffee, juice, pastries, and yogurt--and also had his housekeeper clean our room. We absolutely loved our stay and will definitely be staying w/ Paco when we next go to DF."
