                    "comments": "Outstanding hosts and home! We stayed for 5 days with a group of 7 and the hosts were very friendly and accommodating. The house is gorgeous and we loved all of the different outdoor spaces.  It is very open but private as well.  It is in a great area - we walked to the majority of sites we wanted to see and took the subway as well.  Francisco arranged a trip for us to go to Teotihuacan with the driver.  We also had an incredible breakfast prepared in home that morning to fuel us up.  I would highly recommend that to other guests in the future. \n\nCommunication was easy as both Francisco and Maria Jose were quick to respond with any questions or requests.  I enjoyed meeting them and hope to stay here in the future.  Stay here!! You won't be disappointed."
