                    "reviewerid": "2693279",
                    "reviewer_name": "Yuval",
                    "comments": "Imagine that, an actual Bed-and-Breakfast on AirBnB! The Condesa Haus is run like a traditional bnb and that was quite refreshing. The staff was sweet, attentive, and reliable, serving delicious breakfasts and cleaning the room every night. I stayed in the penthouse and loved it -- it was lovely, very clean, and had an ideal location in beautiful Condesa. The penthouse itself is very private -- just be warned that it requires a hike of many stairs! The kitchen was well-stocked and the bathroom and closet area quite large. I was very happy with my stay and definitely recommend it!"
