                    "reviewerid": "50739566",
                    "reviewer_name": "Carol",
                    "comments": "Lovely Pent House apartment that we booked for my hubby's 50th birthday. We had 15 guests stayed in the other studios/bedrooms and it was a perfect setting for a group visit to CDMX. The pent house was a little smaller than expected, but very chic and perfect for the 2 of us. We also had our guests come up for a surprise nightcap, slideshow and birthday cake after a long birthday meal at Pujol and it fit everyone perfectly! Lucky for us it stopped raining by the end of our trip and we were able to enjoy the roof garden, which has a nice view and lots of recliners/seating. We even had an impromptu dance party up there. Overall a wonderful experience. We can't wait to visit CDMX again--4 days is way too short!! Thank you Condesa Haus!"
