                    "id": "3454072",
                    "date": "2013-02-01",
                    "reviewerid": "4654911",
                    "reviewer_name": "Stacie",
                    "comments": "Four of us were in Mexico City for one week and this apartment proved to be perfect.  The apartment was spacious, well appointed and in a central location close to museums, historic sights, and great food.  Gabriella was very gracious and helpful when we arrived (provided an extra mattress) and was flexible with our check out time.  The building has many amenities and was secure and modern.  I would absolutely stay here again.  Mexico City is now one of my favorite destinations and this apartment was the cherry on top."
