                    "reviewerid": "1967471",
                    "reviewer_name": "Michelle",
                    "comments": "Morgana was an excellent host, lovely to deal with from start to finish, always super quick at replying to messages and really helpful and accommodating. \r\n\r\nThe flat was excellently located, in the heart of Condessa, which second  to neighbouring La Roma is the cool 'hipster' hangout spot in Mexico City at the moment, walking distance to some of the cutest restaurants, coffee shops and cool bars and clubs. The flat is also right opposite a big superama for supplies. \r\n\r\nThe flat is a good size, clean and modern with all the basic amenities you need, very good value for money, I highly recommend this apartment and indeed Morgana. "
