                    "comments": "Morgana was a great host. The apartment was just as advertised. Very clean, comfty, spacious and centrally located. Definitely a great place to stay in la Condesa. \r\n\r\nI recommend you dont miss out on the Condesa Street Market every tuesday on Juan de la Barrera Street!"
