                    "reviewerid": "3540546",
                    "reviewer_name": "Kellie",
                    "comments": "I stayed for five nights in Morgana's apartment, with my husband and our three year old daughter, and while in some ways the apartment is fairly basic, it had everything we needed for a really comfortable and enjoyable stay. The location is superb - you can walk to Chapultepec in a few minutes, there is a supermarket across the road, plus many fantastic restaurants just a short stroll away too. Morgana and her husband are lovely and extremely helpful people. We loved our time staying there, and I'd happily stay there again if we went back. I have no problems in recommending this place for anyone looking for a comfortable and affordable apartment in Condesa."
