                    "reviewerid": "4918178",
                    "reviewer_name": "Rolando",
                    "comments": "Comfy in the Middle of La Condesa was GREAT!!  Morgana and her husband were great and always very responsive to any of my questions or concerns.  The place was clean, organized and in a great neighborhood.  Having a grocery market across the street was really nice.  Plus, they sell tacos de Birria on Saturday and Sunday mornings just up the street which were DELICIOUS!  I would definitely stay again and recommend this apartment to anyone who is interested in staying for vacay."
