                    "reviewerid": "5355918",
                    "reviewer_name": "Flora",
                    "comments": "We had the best experience ever. Morgana's husband Omar greeted us and was very pleasant. Morgana was quick with responding to emails for info that I needed in regards to getting around in the city. The apartment was exactly as she described. The store across the street is perfect it has everything for the whole family. I highly recommend Morgana and her apartment. It was a pleasure Morgana. We hope to be back to Condesa. "
