                    "reviewerid": "1366742",
                    "reviewer_name": "Daniel",
                    "comments": "Wonderful apartment - just what we needed to explore an amazing part of Mexico City, and rest up after an exhausting travel schedule. Would be a fantastic place to stay for a week - full kitchen and amenities, and the wireless internet is fast and reliable. Also, there are GREAT street food options (tortas, tacos, some bean/masa hybrid) within a one block radius.\r\n\r\nMorgana was very responsive and flexible when we needed to make last minute changes to our arrival time. Would definitely come back next time we're in Mexico City."
