                    "comments": "I spent one week in Sandro's flat in Condesa. It was a beautiful, modern, well equipped place, in a fantastic location. Sandro was always willing to help. I think this is the best apartment I have stayed in Mexico City, near parks, cafes, restaurants and bars. It's just a few blocks away from Tamaulipas, which is a street that has lots of fun places to eat and hang out and from \"Parque Espa\u00f1a\" . Another thing that I really liked was the terrace. At night I was able to enjoy it, which was very relaxing. I will definitely stay here again and I highly recommend it!"
