                    "comments": "My boyfriend and I stayed here for a week while visiting DF. Perfect location if you want to be in Roma/Condesa, as we did. It's also a short walk to Chapultepec. The apt is exactly as in the pictures - clean, bright, and very comfortable. Sandro is very accommodating; it could not have been an easier stay. We especially appreciated the beers waiting for us in the fridge! "
